  <T n="entry_text">0xD8096662<!--String: "Electric Lagoon"--></T>
  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0xABCC5779<!--String: "Electric Lagoon, nestled the neighborhood of Crystal Valley, is a mesmerizing haven where glowworms twinkle like tiny stars above the water. The lagoon is famed for its neon jellyfish, the secret ingredient in the local delicacy, Jellyfish Salad. As you swim through the glowing waters, the experience, known as the "Neon Jellyfish Swim," offers not just visual delight but a sense of rejuvenation. It’s a magical blend of nature’s wonders and culinary tradition, inviting all to bask in its enchanting glow."--></T>
